        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3528961092" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1623531075380244650">I read this in University, but I am adding it now on the realisation that it stands on the 1001 list I am working my way through, despite only being a short-story. We were made to read multiple Poe stories alongside (if memory serves) some Doyle stories too, Holmes ones. I preferred Doyle and still do. Though the atmosphere was rather good in the Poe stories, I wasn&apos;t completely invested or enthralled by the stories themselves. </span>
  <span id="freeText1623531075380244650" style="display:none">I read this in University, but I am adding it now on the realisation that it stands on the 1001 list I am working my way through, despite only being a short-story. We were made to read multiple Poe stories alongside (if memory serves) some Doyle stories too, Holmes ones. I preferred Doyle and still do. Though the atmosphere was rather good in the Poe stories, I wasn't completely invested or enthralled by the stories themselves. </span>
