      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/trivia/work/15570165-black-cat-pit-and-the-pendulum-premature-burial-tell-tale-heart">Trivia About The Pit and the P...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
